#Note: zookeeper sasl is not necessary, so zookeeper.properties and zookeeper_jaas.conf can be ignored

###Steps for start kafka server in local:

Assume goreman is installed
0. go get github.com/mattn/goreman

1. Move kafka_server_jaas.conf to $KAFKA_DIR/ (Kafka directory)
2. Move server.X.properties to $KAFKA_DIR/config/
3. Move Procfile to $KAFKA_DIR/
4. Run `goreman start` under $KAFKA_DIR/

Or forget what you read, just set $KAFKA_DIR variable and run ass kicking run.sh (`bash run.sh`)
